decision_conditions: <p>The development hereby approved shall only be carried out in accordance with the following approved plans and documents:</p><ul><li>Justification Statement - Received: 25/07/2023<br></li><li>1188-P-002 - Proposed SitePlan and Existing and Proposed Elevations of Fence - May 2023</li><li>1188-P-005 -Proposed Site plan and Fencing Elevation - July 2023</li></ul><p>No other drawings or documents apply.</p>

The proposed development shall achieve security standards based on Secured by Design principles to the satisfaction of the local authority & Metropolitan Police, details of which shall be provided to the Local Planning Authority for its written approval prior to the first occupation of the approved development. All security measures applied to the approved development shall be permanently retained thereafter.

The development shall be constructed in accordance with the existing fencing materials shown on the photos within 1189-PL-002 - Proposed Site Plan and Existig and Proposed Elevations of the Fence and to the satisfaction of the Local Planning Authority.
The development hereby permitted shall be commenced before the expiration of three years from the date of this permission.
description: Replacement of fencing and gate along north west corner boundary
